1
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:14,800
Sir, please go through security.

2
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:19,120
Okay.

3
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:20,080
This way, please.

4
00:00:22,760 --> 00:00:23,240
Roger that.

5
00:00:23,720 --> 00:00:24,200
Tian Yan,

6
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:25,920
