15
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:54,560
I'm sorry, ma'am.

16
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:55,160
It's a rule.

17
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,200
All metal items

18
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:58,160
