20
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:03,880
Please cooperate.

21
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,120
Hurry up.

22
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:08,800
Please hurry.

23
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,240
Sorry.

24
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,040
I didn't see it.

25
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:31,240
You're good to go.

26
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:31,800
This way.

27
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:40,920
Excuse me.

28
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,600
Please go through the security check.

29
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:46,760
Ms. Tian.

30
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,400
Let's go sit over there.

31
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,040
