32
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,240
No.

33
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:55,960
Thank you.

34
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,680
Please, Brother Fu.

35
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,320
You two

36
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:17,760
