39
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,720
Wait for me.

40
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,040
Your earring.

41
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:30,640
Sorry.

42
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,120
You dropped your earring.

43
