54
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,680
Ah,

55
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:07,440
I remember the last time at our Fengyue Villa,

56
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:10,440
Brother Fu, you scolded me because of a waitress.

57
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:12,040
