92
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:16,920
And they

93
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,480
enjoy it immensely.

94
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,120
After all, compared to you,

95
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,600
I know Miss Tianyan

96
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,360
of Tianyan

97
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:26,960
than you.

98
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,800
It seems that Mr. Fu

99
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,520
is still thinking about her,

100
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,080
so much so that

101
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,800
he remembers her so clearly.

102
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,520
Excuse me,

103
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,480
I have something to talk to

104
