110
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,440
I can't help it.

111
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,960
I just want to see you more.

112
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,120
Because I don't know

113
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,840
