158
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,200
Thank you.

159
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:29,920
It's a pity that you are an illegitimate child.

160
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,160
I can't hand over the

161
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,840
