173
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,280
Now I'm also very disappointed in him.

174
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,760
He's been fooled by a woman.

175
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:03,840
What should I do?

176
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:07,120
I have to take back the Silver Light Hall myself.

177
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,200
Back then,

178
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,520
you used me

179
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,840
and controlled my mother,

180
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,440
making her a scapegoat.

181
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,600
You drugged her,

182
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:21,920
made her crazy,

183
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,120
and killed her.

184
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:25,920
For so many years,

185
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:28,600
I followed your teachings.

186
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,520
Family.

187
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:31,680
Sacrifice.

188
00:09:37,560 --> 00:09:38,400
Father.

189
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:41,080
I've worked so hard

190
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,480
to turn your trick

191
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,760
