192
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:48,520
to tell you today that

193
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,680
I won't become like you.

194
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:52,000
He did it on purpose.

195
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,320
His purpose

196
