204
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:15,240
Would it?

205
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:19,600
Brother Fu,

206
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,120
as you instructed,

207
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:21,720
I looked into

208
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,720
