219
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,680
Yes,

220
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:44,240
he came back two years ago.

221
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:46,120
But he's been keeping a low profile.

222
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:51,320
Yellow Bourbon,

223
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:52,320
