224
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:54,200
People here aren't used to it.

225
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,360
But

226
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:58,280
I like the bitter taste.

227
00:10:58,920 --> 00:10:59,760
Mr. Cheng,

228
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:01,000
