246
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:28,680
What's the situation now?

247
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:31,480
It's me.

248
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:35,400
You've worked so hard to trap me,

249
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,120
