255
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:54,640
Let her go!

256
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:55,720
What's this?

257
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,480
Feeling sorry for her, huh?

258
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:58,280
It's my turn.

259
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:02,680
It's my turn.

260
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:06,640
You feel sorry for her?

261
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:08,040
Let her go.

262
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:17,600
Let him go.

263
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,520
IPCO will be here soon.

264
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:20,680
Tian Yan.

265
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,000
Put on your clothes.

266
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,440
Don't catch a cold.

267
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,600
What do you mean?

268
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,160
Put on your clothes.

269
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:35,480
inside.

270
00:12:36,680 --> 00:12:37,560
Don't let others see it.

271
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:40,960
Guess

272
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,800
