273
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:45,960
Tian Yan.

274
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:46,880
Shoot.

275
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:51,120
Don't move.

276
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:53,040
Cover your head.

277
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:53,760
Cover your head with both hands.

278
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:55,560
Cover your head with both hands.

279
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:56,840
Shoot.

280
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,000
Don't forget, I killed your master.

281
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:07,560
I told you.

282
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:10,040
Don't be soft.

283
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:38,400
Let go of me.

284
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,320
Let go of me.

285
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:42,720
[As we enter the new millennium together,]

286
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:45,520
[the world is full of expectations and blessings for the future.]

287
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:46,720
[However,]

288
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:48,360
[at the local millennium celebration,]

289
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:50,400
[sad news came.]

290
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,680
[The heir of the Yinguangtang Group,]

291
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:53,560
[Pang Jingfu,]

292
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:55,800
